[{"id":"72","text":"怎么了？"},{"id":"72","text":"......"},{"id":"72","text":"你的表情很难看。"}],"values":[],"id":71},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":72,"end":132},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_395_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"你感受不到，你不是萨卡兹。","id":74,"figure":"avg_npc_395_1#10$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_395_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"我们......在面对自己的历史。在面对萨卡兹千万年的苦难。","id":76,"figure":"avg_npc_395_1#10$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_395_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"它在诉说，它在愤怒，它强迫我们每个人聆听它的悲号。","id":78,"figure":"avg_npc_395_1#2$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_395_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......怪不得。","id":80,"figure":"avg_npc_395_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"哼，大公爵们要失望了，这并非什么可被复制的工业技术。","id":81,"figure":"avg_npc_395_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"这艘船，是一位死魂灵。","id":82,"figure":"avg_npc_395_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":83},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":84},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":85},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":86},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"萨卡兹是怎么生活的？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":87},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"在最开始的时候，萨卡兹是怎么生活的？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":88},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"那时，神民与先民还没有侵入这片大地，这里的一切还是它本该是的样子。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":89},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"然后，他们来了。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":90},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"他们开始杀伐，他们开始屠戮，他们把野蛮与愤怒带进了我们的土地，他们不光把爪牙指向彼此，也指向我们。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":91},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"骄傲的萨卡兹怎么会向他们屈服，我们必须还击。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":92},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"我们以更盛大的愤怒回报他们，他们必须吞下仇恨的果实！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":93},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"可是，为什么好像只是一转眼的时间，卡兹戴尔就被毁灭了？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":94},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"那些卑鄙者！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":95},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"他们用尽了方法，他们想遍了招数！他们卑劣而狡诈，他们无耻而残忍！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":96},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"他们凭什么践踏纯洁的卡兹戴尔？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":97},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"他们有什么资格！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":98},{"type":"subtitle","id":99},{"type":"Dialog","id":100},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":101},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":102},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":103},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"呜——","id":104,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#11$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":105},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我......这些声音......","id":106,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#11$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_395_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":107},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"阿米娅，别被它影响！","id":108,"figure":"avg_npc_395_1#3$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_395_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":109},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"坚持住，这只是幻象！","id":110,"figure":"avg_npc_395_1#3$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#15$1","focus":"m","id":111},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我明白，我在尝试......","id":112,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#15$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":113},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"呜呜——啊——","id":114,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#11$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":115},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":116},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":117},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"卡兹戴尔被毁灭了。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":118},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"魔王与王庭带领我们与那些渣滓战斗，萨卡兹不会承认这种可耻的失败。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":119},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"但是懦弱的自称萨科塔的萨卡兹逃避了他们的责任，他们背叛了自己的种族，背叛了自己的使命！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":120},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"刚刚重建的高墙再次崩溃，我们的梦想再次消亡。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":121},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"没关系，叛徒会被清算，卡兹戴尔会再次矗立。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":122},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"只要魔王还站在我们的身前，我们就不会被击溃。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":123},{"type":"subtitle","id":124},{"type":"Dialog","id":125},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":126},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":127},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":128},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"这里的影子......","id":129,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"不对，这不是和那位伊内丝小姐类似的操纵阴影的源石技艺，这是什么？","id":130,"figure":"avg_npc_867_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_395_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":131},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"博士，离开飞空艇的影子！","id":132,"figure":"avg_npc_395_1#3$1","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":133},{"type":"charslot","id":134},{"type":"Text","text":"飞空艇的阴影蠕动着，延展着，被阿斯卡纶击倒在地的另一名“灰礼帽”瞬间淹没在漆黑的海洋中。","id":135},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“灰礼帽”","text":"开什么玩笑，这到底是什么......","id":136},{"type":"Text","text":"深重的黑色，深重的绝望，深重的愤怒。","id":137},{"type":"Dialog","id":138},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":139},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":140},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"魔王会带领我们，只要有魔王......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":141},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"卡兹戴尔被毁灭了三十四次。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":142},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"卡兹戴尔被毁灭了六百七十五次。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":143},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"卡兹戴尔被毁灭了三千四百二十一次。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":144},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"最短暂的一次，卡兹戴尔的城墙刚刚重建仅仅三天，天马的铁蹄就再次把这里碾为齑粉。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":145},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"卡兹戴尔一次又一次被毁灭，一次又一次重新建立。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":146},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"时间改变了我们的形貌，也扭曲了他们的长相，但战争从未结束，我们从未停止抵抗。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":147},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"但我们重建卡兹戴尔所花的时间也越来越长。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":148},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"我们的文明被摧残，我们的艺术被遗忘。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":149},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"但是还有仇恨，魔王以仇恨作为武器，斩杀我们的敌人！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":150},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"我以此为傲，我以我们的不屈为傲。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":151},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"然而今天，瞧瞧我看到了什么？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":152},{"type":"subtitle","id":153},{"type":"Dialog","id":154},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":155},{"type":"Background","id":156},{"type":"Image","image":"37_i10","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","id":157},{"type":"ImageTween","xFrom":"0","yFrom":"30","xTo":"0","yTo":"0","xScaleFrom":"1.1","yScaleFrom":"1.1","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"8","block":"false","id":158},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":159},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":160},{"type":"delay","time":"4","id":161},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":162},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"一个扭曲的奇美拉......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":163},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"一个异族的魔王？！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":164},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"哈哈哈哈，我的面前，站着一位异族的魔王？！！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":165},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"你凭什么拥有这顶王冠？你凭什么与这些痛苦站在一起？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":166},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"你凭什么配承载萨卡兹的愤怒！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":167},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"回答我！顶替者！回答我，骗徒！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":168},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"回答死魂灵的质问！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":169},{"type":"subtitle","id":170},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":171},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"死魂灵......","id":172},{"type":"dialog","id":173},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":174},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"去看！睁大你的眼睛去看！虚假的魔王！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":175},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"你看到了什么？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":176},{"type":"subtitle","id":177},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":178},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#18$1","focus":"m","id":179},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我看到了......","id":180,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#18$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_395_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":181},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"别去看，阿米娅，那是死魂灵的巫术！","id":182,"figure":"avg_npc_395_1#3$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#18$1","focus":"m","id":183},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":184,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#18$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#18$1","focus":"m","id":185},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我看到了泪水。","id":186,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#18$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#18$1","focus":"m","id":187},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"死魂灵，我看到了如此沉重的悲伤。","id":188,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#18$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#18$1","focus":"m","id":189},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"您一直与这些悲伤在一起吗？","id":190,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#18$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":191},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":192},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"悲伤？这不是悲伤。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":193},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"我早已不再悲伤。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":194},{"type":"subtitle","id":195},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":196},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#18$1","focus":"m","id":197},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"您用愤怒的火焰灼烧伤口。","id":198,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#18$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#18$1","focus":"m","id":199},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"这......很痛苦。","id":200,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#18$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":201},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":202},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"我认得清什么是真实，什么是虚假！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":203},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"你只需回答我的问题！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":204},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"你——凭什么——","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":205},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"你——一个该死的扭曲的异族人——","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":206},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"凭——什——么——","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":207},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"背负萨卡兹的一切！！！！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":208},{"type":"subtitle","id":209},{"type":"Dialog","id":210},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":211},{"type":"Image","id":212},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":213},{"type":"charslot","id":214},{"type":"Background","image":"37_g7_airshipdock","screenadapt":"coverall","id":215},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":216},{"type":"Text","text":"阿斯卡纶踉跄了几步。","id":217},{"type":"dialog","id":218},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"220","text":"你没事吧，阿斯卡纶？"}],"values":[],"id":219},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":220,"end":224},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_395_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":221},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"我......还好......","id":222,"figure":"avg_npc_395_1#10$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_395_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":223},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"阿米娅她——","id":224,"figure":"avg_npc_395_1#10$1","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":225},{"type":"charslot","id":226},{"type":"Text","text":"死魂灵巨大的阴影里，阿米娅仍然昂着头。","id":227},{"type":"Text","text":"在这个角度，看不到阿米娅的表情，唯一能知道的是，她仍昂着头。","id":228},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":229},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"您说得对，死魂灵。我应该去看，我看见了。","id":230,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":231},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我看见了这一切。","id":232,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":233},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我看见了那三千四百二十一次毁灭，我看见了每一片砖瓦化为灰烬。","id":234,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":235},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我看见了每一位魔王的反抗，我看见了他们每一个人的心。","id":236,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":237},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我看到了那些被吞咽的泪水和鲜血，我看到了那些被高扬起的尘土和碎片。","id":238,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":239},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......如此相似的身影交叠着倒下，如此相似的场景反复上演。","id":240,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":241},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我看到了，我仍然选择去看，我还会继续看下去。","id":242,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":243},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"死魂灵，我没有一刻移开目光。","id":244,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":245},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我会牢牢记住。","id":246,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":247},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我会记住每一次艰难的选择，每一次的死亡与牺牲，每一次的毁灭，每一次的希望。","id":248,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","id":249},{"type":"dialog","id":250},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":251},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"——是我让你看见的，奇美拉。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":252},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"是我逼着你去看的！！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":253},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"顶替者，我没有一刻不在亲历，我没有一刻不在被这烈火煎熬！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":254},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"可是你呢？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":255},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"当然，你可以去看，像看一幅地图，像看一出戏剧，像一个高踞在悬崖上的，漠视着我们的看客。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":256},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"虚假的魔王，我斥责你，我痛恨你，不是因为你的愚蠢，不是因为你的狂妄，不是因为你的自以为是。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":257},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"而是因为，你永远不可能真正与我们站在一起。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":258},{"type":"subtitle","id":259},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":260},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#15$1","focus":"m","id":261},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"可我已经在努力——","id":262,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#15$1"},{"type":"charslot","id":263},{"type":"dialog","id":264},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":265},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"努力？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":266},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"你可以努力不移开目光——","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":267},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"但你仍可以随时转身离去。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":268},{"type":"subtitle","id":269},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":270},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#14$1","focus":"m","id":271},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我......","id":272,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#14$1"},{"type":"charslot","id":273},{"type":"dialog","id":274},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":275},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"你不是萨卡兹，你就永远不是萨卡兹。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":276},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"萨卡兹的众魂不会接纳你。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":277},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"你称我们的境遇为痛苦？你说你可以努力忍受——","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":278},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"可我们命定被这一切所永恒浸没。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":279},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"你声称你有勇气，但倘若有一天，你无法再咽下这些苦难......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":280},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"你仍可以舍我们而去。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":281},{"type":"subtitle","id":282},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":283},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#15$1","focus":"m","id":284},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"可是，我一定不会——","id":285,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#15$1"},{"type":"charslot","id":286},{"type":"dialog","id":287},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":288},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"你才跨越多少岁月，你居然敢于声称“一定”？！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":289},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"不，你会的，因为你有这个能力，所以你一定会。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":290},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"萨卡兹怎么可能选择这样一位魔王，萨卡兹怎么可能接纳这样一位魔王？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":291},{"type":"subtitle","id":292},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":293},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":294},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"特蕾西娅小姐希望我能成为......！她说，就算是异族，我们依然会感同身受！","id":295,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#7$1"},{"type":"charslot","id":296},{"type":"dialog","id":297},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":298},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"这就是她的愚蠢之处！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":299},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"那么，倘若你真的感同身受......在你看过了这一切之后......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":300},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"你为什么还会走到我的面前？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":301},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"你为什么还会试图阻止这场战争？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":302},{"type":"subtitle","id":303},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":304},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#14$1","focus":"m","id":305},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我......","id":306,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#14$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":307},{"type":"charslot","id":308},{"type":"Text","text":"阿米娅突然发现自己无法说出一个字。","id":309},{"type":"Text","text":"她为什么要阻止这场战争？","id":310},{"type":"Text","text":"在看了这些愤恨，这些痛苦，这些渴求之后。","id":311},{"type":"Text","text":"她为什么要阻止这场战争？","id":312},{"type":"Text","text":"这......这场战争，对于萨卡兹而言，确实是唯一的方法。","id":313},{"type":"Text","text":"每一个萨卡兹，在面对了这一切之后，都无法得出其他答案。",